title: All 17 'People Like Us' Radio Shows (Comedy)
description:
The original 1995-97 BBC radio shows that came before the TV series.

Chris Langham plays the hapless interviewer Roy Mallard in this comedy &#039;Mockumentary&#039; where he meets everyday folk at their places of work.

All 17 episodes from 3 radio series including a Christmas special.
